PrecisRegulations Amending the CIFTA TARIFF PREFERENCE REGULATIONS by obliging importers to provide documentary evidence, upon request, that goods shipped to Canada through the United States did not undergo any further processing within U.S. territory that would increase their value by more than 10%.

precis:
Regulations Amending the CIFTA TARIFF PREFERENCE REGULATIONS by obliging
importers to provide documentary evidence, upon request, that goods shipped
to Canada through the United States did not undergo any further processing
within U.S. territory that would increase their value by more than 10%.
